<plot>Widowmaker is the story of a mysterious woman who constantly relives her past in the present through a series of murders with a sexual edge. Unable to escape her demons on her own, a tentative and tenuous new friendship with a ten-year-old homeless girl offers her the key to her salvation. But will she use it? Can she save this little girl, and in the process save herself?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?656158</url></doc>
